            <lg xml:id="TK681">
<l>aṉpuṭaimai yāṉṟa kuṭippiṟattal vēntavām</l>
<l>paṇpuṭaimai tūturaippāṉ paṇpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The qualification of an ambassador are affection (for his relations) a fitting birth, and the possession of attributes pleasing to royalty.</l>
            </lg>
